---
title: Pronto Chicken White Pizzas with Baby Broccoli, Fresh Mozzarella, and Tuscan Herbs
description: Consider your pizza fix fixed! With this recipe, you’ll have a pie with a flatbread crust piled high with pieces of chicken, plump tomatoes, crunchy bites of baby broccoli, and gooey mozzarella. It’s baked under the broiler to give it a crispy, golden-edged finish that will make everyone ooh and ahh as it’s brought to the table. Oh, and we should mention the best part: it’ll be done in just twenty minutes.
